Locales for the Croogo CMS <http://www.croogo.org>

Installation:

1. Download or Clone this Repo.
2. Go to your Admin Panel and upload the <LANG>.zip


ATTENTION!:
The offical Croogo local directory structure starts in the language folder. Exsample: locales/german/<here croogo directory>.
Just zip that directory and upload it to Croogo with the help of the local extension. Exsample: in locales/german you zip the folder "deu".


Locales:

german -  german translation of the default.po. 


